				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Twisting Made Easy<a name="33066"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 5 04 10:14 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I am a lazy bard... That being said I dont want to spend all my time using the mouse to twist my songs.
<br />

<br />
How to twist with a hot button.
<br />

<br />
line 1   /pause 30,/cast 1
<br />
line 2   /stop
<br />
line 3   /pause 30,/cast 2
<br />
line 4   /stop
<br />
line 5   /cast 3
<br />

<br />
Now this will twist the first 3 songs on your spell gems but will not stop the 3rd song. u will have to make a button to stop or click that one time to stop the song and hit your hotbutton again to keep the twist.
<br />

<br />
I know this only twist 3 songs but there are just days i dont want to do that much work (every day) and it gives me time to talk if i want to.
<br />

<br />
Hope this helps 
<br />
Ziyon 65 Bard TM</span></td>
